@section topSection{
    <div class="only-homepage-element">
        <div>
            <h4 style="text-align: center">COVID-19</h4>
            <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 80%">This rapidly evolving corona virus (COVID-19) has imposed an unsettling, fluid situation upon our community and its business. The team at Becket & Lee is maintaining our services as we make adjustments to how we are performing those services to protect the health and safety of our staff and their families and comply with all government orders. We are working with our clients to adjust our process to meet their evolving needs while also keeping them up to date as to the impacts, and projected impacts, to the bankruptcy system. </p>
        </div>
    </div>
}

